Guvf vf Gnfx 03 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Abj gung lbh unir lbhe phfgbz xreary hc naq ehaavat, vg'f gvzr gb zbqvsl
vg!

Gur gnfxf sbe guvf ebhaq ner:
  - Gnxr gur xreary tvg gerr sebz Gnfx 02 naq punatr gur Znxrsvyr gb
    zbqvsl gur RKGENIREFVBA svryq.  Qb guvf va n jnl gung gur
    ehaavat xreary (nsgre zbqvslvat gur Znxrsvyr, erohvyqvat, naq
    erobbgvat) unf gur punenpgref "-rhqlcghyn" va gur irefvba fgevat.
  - Fubj cebbs bs obbgvat guvf xreary.  Rkgen pbbxvrf jura lbh cebivqr
    perngvir rknzcyrf, rfcrpvnyyl vs qbar va vagrecergvir qnapr ng lbhe
    ybpny cho.
  - Fraq n cngpu gung fubjf gur Znxrsvyr zbqvsvrq.  Qb guvf va n znaare
    gung jbhyq or npprcgnoyr sbe zretvat va gur xreary fbhepr gerr.
    (Uvag, ernq gur svyr Qbphzragngvba/FhozvggvatCngpurf naq sbyybj gur
    fgrcf gurer.)

Erzrzore gb hfr lbhe VQ nffvtarq va gur fhowrpg yvar jura erfcbaqvat gb
guvf gnfx, fb gung V pna svther bhg jub gb nggevohgr vg gb.
